      "id": "ml98p42v",
      "questionNumber": 5,
      "questionText": "<p>$$ \\text { Consider the following two reactions } \\mathrm{A} \\text { and } \\mathrm{B} \\text {. } $$</p>\n<p><img alt=\"JEE Main 2026 (Online) 24th January Morning Shift Chemistry - Aldehydes, Ketones and Carboxylic Acids Question 15 English\" src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/6y3zli1ml9cf37x/af284689-24af-469e-8b04-05efd3fec675/91931bd0-0281-11f1-8e98-edf480d810c9/file-6y3zli1ml9cf37y.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/6y3zli1ml9cf37x/af284689-24af-469e-8b04-05efd3fec675/91931bd0-0281-11f1-8e98-edf480d810c9/file-6y3zli1ml9cf37y.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\"></p>\n<p>Numerical value of [molar mass of $x+$ molar mass of $y$ ] is $\\_\\_\\_\\_$</p>",
      "options": [
        "<p>46</p>\n<p></ol></p>",
        "<p>160</p>",
        "<p>88</p>",
        "<p>4</p>"
